fields.title: 2020 Trip Out West
fields.description: Our trip out west lasted 5 days, and was spent at the Grand Canyon, Bryce Canyon, and Zion National Park.

fields.title: 2021 Family Trip to Florida
fields.description: Took a trip to Destin, Fl with my parents. Spent 4 days there, kayaking to the natural springs was the best part.
